#: .\templates\registration\activation_email.txt:3
msgid "Hi,"
msgstr "你好"

#: .\templates\registration\activate.html:8
msgid "Account activation failed."
msgstr "帐户激活失败。"

#: .\templates\registration\activate.html:9
msgid ""
"Your account may have been activated, please contact us if you are unable to"
" activate your account"
msgstr "您的帐户可能已被激活，如果您无法激活您的帐户，请联系我们"

#: .\templates\registration\activate.html:11
#: .\templates\registration\activation_email.txt:18
msgid "Sincerely,"
msgstr "真诚"

#: .\templates\registration\activation_email.txt:5
msgid ""
"You (or someone pretending to be you) have asked to register an account at"
msgstr "您（或冒充您的人）已要求在"

#: .\templates\registration\activation_email.txt:6
msgid ""
"If this wasn't you, please ignore this email and your address will be "
"removed from our records."
msgstr "如果这不是您，请忽略此电子邮件，您的地址将从我们的记录中删除。"

#: .\templates\registration\activation_email.txt:9
msgid ""
"Your account has been created, please activate your account by clicking the "
"link below."
msgstr "您的帐户已创建，请点击下面的链接激活您的帐户。"

#: .\templates\registration\activation_email.txt:13
msgid "Link is valid for 24 hours."
msgstr "链接的有效期为 24 小时。"

#: .\templates\registration\activation_email.txt:15
msgid ""
"Before logging in, you must activate your account, Once your account has "
"been activated, please update your personal profile."
msgstr "登录前，您必须激活您的帐户，帐户激活后，请更新您的个人个人资料。"

#: .\templates\registration\activation_email.txt:16
msgid "If you have any questions, please contact us."
msgstr "如果您有任何问题，请联系我们。"
